title: Videohive - Business Reel [TeEtOs]
description:
After Effects CS4 and above project file. Great visual effects and animation. The template perfectly fits for creating corporate intros, business promos and presentations. I hope you like it! :)



100% After Effects
Original concept
Trapcode Particular plug-in is required. The project was created with using Trapcode Particular, Shine and VC Optical Flares plug-ins. But the download includes pre-rendered version of the project, so you don`t need Trapcode Shine and VC Optical Flares plug-ins
22 textholders
About 50 video/image places
Logo placeholder
1 min. 50 sec. duration
Video tutorial shows you how to customize this template
